    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You release a powerful chakra line, manifesting spectral claws that slash through the affected area.<br />Every creature within a 60 ft. long and 5 ft. wide line must make a Dexterity saving throw, on a failure, they take 6d8 slashing damage and a rank of bleed, or half as much on a success.</p><p>    <strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> for each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, the chakra cost increases by 3, the damage increases by 1d8, the line's length increases by 10 ft., and the width increases by 5ft.</p>",
